   <text:p text:style-name="P55"><text:soft-page-break/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#noteref.2.34.1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">c</text:span></text:a>Â A. A encourager le luxe et Ã  flatter la mollesse.</text:p>
