   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#noteref.7-26.1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">1</text:span></text:a>Â Le duc de La Force.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P55"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#noteref.7-30.1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">2</text:span></text:a>Â M. Bouillet, mÃ©decin Ã  BÃ©ziers. (1690-1777.)</text:p>
