   <text:p text:style-name="P55"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#noteref.7.315.2" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">2</text:span></text:a>Â Sur tous ces personnages qui composaient la sociÃ©tÃ© de M<text:span text:style-name="T2">me</text:span> Du Deffand, on trouvera des dÃ©tails curieux dans la <text:span text:style-name="T1">Correspondance inÃ©dite de Madame Du Deffand</text:span>, Paris, 1818, 2 vol. in-8Âº.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P55"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#noteref.7.315.3" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">3</text:span></text:a>Â Le prÃ©sident HÃ©nault.</text:p>
