   <text:p text:style-name="P55"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#noteref.7.332.3" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">3</text:span></text:a>Â On appelle <text:span text:style-name="T1">toste</text:span>, en Angleterre, les santÃ©s des personnes absentes, que lâon se porte rÃ©ciproquement, et que lâon ne peut refuser sans impolitesse. (Note de lâÃ©dition de Paris 1767.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P55"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#noteref.7.333.1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">4</text:span></text:a>Â Le roi de Prusse, FrÃ©dÃ©ric II.</text:p>
