   <text:p text:style-name="P55">Grand roi, cesse de vaincre, ou je cesse dâÃ©crire<text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#note.7.347.1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition"><text:span text:style-name="T2">2</text:span></text:span></text:a>Â ;</text:p>
