   <text:p text:style-name="P55"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#noteref.7.387.3" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">3</text:span></text:a>Â CÃ©lÃ¨bre mÃ©decin de Bordeaux.</text:p>
